</subtitle><author><name>toshimaru</name></author><entry><title type="html">Using less without word-wrap</title><link href="https://blog.toshima.ru/2017/08/08/less-without-word-wrap.html" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Using less without word-wrap" /><published>2017-08-08T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2017-08-08T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://blog.toshima.ru/2017/08/08/less-without-word-wrap</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://blog.toshima.ru/2017/08/08/less-without-word-wrap.html">&lt;p&gt;When you open up a file with less, word-wrap is sometimes annoying.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;language-terminal highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;gp&quot;&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;w&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;less longtext.txt
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;amp-img src=&quot;/images/less1.png&quot; alt=&quot;less1&quot; width=&apos;1110&apos; height=&apos;860&apos; layout=&apos;responsive&apos;&gt;&lt;/amp-img&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;You can open it without word-wrap by passing &lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;-S&lt;/code&gt; option.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;language-terminal highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;gp&quot;&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;w&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;less &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;-S&lt;/span&gt; longtext.txt
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;amp-img src=&quot;/images/less2.png&quot; alt=&quot;less2&quot; width=&apos;1250&apos; height=&apos;716&apos; layout=&apos;responsive&apos;&gt;&lt;/amp-img&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

